title: Independent candidate Ayaz Ahmad wins PP-222 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Ayaz Ahmad has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-222, Multan-X by securing 30,579 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Peoples Party Parliamentarian (PPPP) Rana Tahir Shabbir, who bagged 28,702 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.29%.
